OL,3,CEx-police officer holds back tears as
OL,4,Che recalls impact of Novichok poisoning
OL,6,FA former police officer who was
OL,7,Fpoisoned by Novichok held back tears
OL,8,Fas he gave evidence to the Dawn
OL,9,FSturgess Inquiry about how the
OL,10,Fincident had affected him mentally and
OL,11,Fphysically.
OL,13,FNick Bailey, who was a Detective
OL,14,FSergeant at the time, was contaminated
OL,15,Fafter the nerve agent was smeared on
OL,16,Fformer Russian spy Sergei Skripal's
OL,17,Fdoor handle in Salisbury in March 2018.
OL,19,FThe poisoning of Mr Bailey followed
OL,20,Fthe attempted murder of Mr Skripal and
OL,21,Fhis daughter Yulia.
