OL,3,CEx-police officer holds back tears as
OL,4,Che recalls impact of Novichok poisoning
OL,6,FIt also came a few months before Ms
OL,7,FSturgess, 44, died after being exposed
OL,8,Fto Novichok left in a discarded
OL,9,Fperfume bottle in nearby Amesbury,
OL,10,FWiltshire.
OL,12,FQuestioning Mr Bailey on his
OL,13,Frecollection of events on Thursday,
OL,14,Fcounsel to the inquiry Francesca
OL,15,FWhitelaw KC said: "It is fair to say
OL,16,Fthe poisoning had a very significant
OL,17,Fmental and physical impact on you."
OL,19,FMr Bailey appeared to well up as he
OL,20,Fnodded in response to Ms Whitelaw.
