OL,3,CEx-police officer holds back tears as
OL,4,Che recalls impact of Novichok poisoning
OL,6,FAt the beginning of his evidence, Mr
OL,7,FBailey said: "My recollection of the
OL,8,Fevents of March 2018 is hazy at best.
OL,10,F"I spent a lot of time dealing with it
OL,11,Fwhen it happened and dealing with the
OL,12,Faftermath of it, processing it, and I
OL,13,Fgot to a point where the only way for
OL,14,Fme to kind of move on from it was to
OL,15,Fstop thinking about it and to close it
OL,16,Foff.
OL,18,F"So it's been some time since I have
OL,19,Factually had to then go back to those
OL,20,Fevents ` so yes, my memory of the
OL,21,Fincident isn't the best."
