OL,3,CEx-police officer holds back tears as
OL,4,Che recalls impact of Novichok poisoning
OL,6,FMr Bailey was then asked to recall
OL,7,Fentering Mr Skripal's address,
OL,8,Fdetailing everything he touched in the
OL,9,Fhouse.
OL,11,FHe also spoke of how his symptoms
OL,12,Fworsened overnight after being
OL,13,Fpoisoned, with him feeling "incredibly
OL,14,Fhot" and sweating.
OL,16,FHe said: "Overnight, I would describe
OL,17,Fit as getting a lot worse.
OL,19,F"I went down at around five in the
OL,20,Fmorning because I was freaking out a
OL,21,Flittle and my vision was impaired.
